                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18211205-162-defend1659 t18211205-162-deflabel1000"></join>. On the 8th of November, between twelve and one o'clock he came and asked where the cart was gone, and said he was going to meet it, he asked me to fetch him some beer, I was gone a few minutes, and saw him come from the lump room, towards the warehouse door, he appeared bulky; I followed and saw a loaf of sugar in his bosom - he begged to be let go. I got him back with difficulty.</p>
